data.chText: 她把家里收拾得一尘不染。
他的操行记录至今无任何污点。
data.enText: He has a spotless record so far.

value.def: Something that is spotless is completely clean.

example.ex: Each morning cleaners make sure everything is spotless...
example.tran: 每天早晨，清洁工们会把一切都打扫得干干净净。

example.ex: Even in the most spotless homes, carpets need regular cleaning to keep them looking good.
example.tran: 即便是在最干净的房子里，地毯也需要定期清洁以保持美观。

value.tran: 极其干净的;一尘不染的

example.ex: The house had huge, spotlessly clean rooms.
example.tran: 房子里的各个房间都很宽敞、一尘不染。
